  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Perception +6</strong></p><p><strong>Communication </strong>telepathic (only with user, in languages they understand)</p><p><strong>Skills </strong>Nature +6, Stealth +6</p><p><strong>Int </strong>+0, <strong>Wis </strong>+2, <strong>Cha </strong>+3</p><p><strong>Will (Ego) </strong>+16</p><hr /><p>A one handed sword almost resembling a long knife made for cutting meat, designed for cutting and thrusting.</p><p>It is crafted out of a special and rare material known only as soulsteel - a dark, nearly black metal with veins of silver - that is difficult to work due to its more volatile properties.</p><p>Soulsteel pulls at both the lifeforce of the living, and the energy that animates the undead, wielder and foe ailke. A skilled magical crafter can help attune this material to a particular user, usually someone who is a decent mage in their own right, so that it doesn't harm them.</p><p>A weapon crafted of this material deals 1 extra spirit damage. At 6th level, this damage is replaced by an @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.6llILJtsTPgtYXgx]{Astral} rune; this rune cannot be removed, and it deals 1d8 damage instead of 1d6 damage. At 14th level, this weapon automatically gains a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.hebf5k3cd7LO6luX]{Astral (Greater)} rune instead. It is also able to affect incorporeal creatures as if it had the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.JQdwHECogcTzdd8R]{Ghost Touch} rune. However, creatures other than those attuned to this weapon cannot handle it without feeling a sense of unease, and the weapon pulling at their lifeforce. Incorporeal creatures cannot touch it without feeling great pain, dropping it immediately.</p><hr /><p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p><p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p><ul><li><strong>Cantrip</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.gYjPm7YwGtEa1oxh]{Ray of Frost}</li><li><strong>1st</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.XSujb7EsSwKl19Uu]{Bless}</li></ul><hr /><p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> You have the magus's Spellstrike activity. Supply one casting of all listed ranks of all listed spells.</p><hr /><p><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:auto !important;scrollbar-color:initial;color:rgb(231, 209, 177);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:17.5px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgba(6, 4, 3, 0.92);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">Restless - </strong>Slowly moves and fidgets.</span></p>"
    },
